NEXT STEP-: 
The sight of the glimmering object on the pedestal pulls you toward it, your curiosity piqued. The chamber feels ancient, the walls adorned with faded murals depicting long-forgotten scenes of Atlantis. The water is eerily still, and the silence weighs heavy on you. As you swim closer, the object comes into clearer focus—it appears to be a glowing crystal, pulsating faintly as if alive.

However, something about the pedestal feels off. The floor surrounding it is littered with broken stones, almost as if something—or someone—has been here before. The crystal’s glow intensifies, casting strange shadows around the room.
